/li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Rogar_Jaehaerys_and_Vermithor.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2e/Rogar_Jaehaerys_and_Vermithor.JPG/350px-Rogar_Jaehaerys_and_Vermithor.JPG\" width=\"350\" height=\"518\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2e/Rogar_Jaehaerys_and_Vermithor.JPG/525px-Rogar_Jaehaerys_and_Vermithor.JPG 1.5x, /images/2/2e/Rogar_Jaehaerys_and_Vermithor.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Rogar_Jaehaerys_and_Vermithor.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jaehaerys showing Vermithor to Rogar, as depicted by Douglas Wheatley in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>.</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Year 50 After the Conquest</b> (<b>50 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 50th after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> that maesters and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>Regent Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa</a> and the Hand <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a> ruled in King's Landing, trying to find a way to undo the secret marriage of <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne</a>. When they failed and the realm began to be aware of their union, they clashed and Alyssa dismissed her husband from his position of Hand of the King. On the ninth moon of the year, Jaehaerys came of age and flew to King's Landing to assume the rule of the realm in person.\n</p><p>In the Wall, two former knights of the Kingsguard lead a rebellion of former <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a>. The uprising was short-lived, but Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Stark_(Lord)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Walton Stark (Lord)\">Walton Stark</a> died in the fight.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Deaths\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Deaths</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Titles_and_Positions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Titles and Positions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=50_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Olyver_Bracken\" title=\"Olyver Bracken\">Olyver Bracken</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raymund_Mallery\" title=\"Raymund Mallery\">Raymund Mallery</a>, the former Kingsguard of <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor</a> that had been sent to the wall by Jaehaerys, rebel against the Watch and try to establish themselves as lords in the castles of <a href=\"/index.php/Rimegate\" title=\"Rimegate\">Rimegate</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Sable_Hall\" title=\"Sable Hall\">Sable Hall</a>. Most of the rebels were former <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a> that had been sent to the Wall, but only a tenth of the men of the Watch joined them. The revolt is terminated quickly, due the loyalty of most men of the Watch and the help of House Stark.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Orryn_Baratheon\" title=\"Orryn Baratheon\">Orryn Baratheon</a> is captured by the High Septon while attempting to kidnap <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaella_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aegon)\" title=\"Rhaella Targaryen (daughter of Aegon)\">Rhaella Targaryen</a>.</li>\n<li>On the 15th day of the 6th moon, Ser Howard Bullock abandons his wife and leaves Dragonstone with <a href=\"/index.php/Coryanne_Wylde\" title=\"Coryanne Wylde\">Coryanne Wylde</a>.</li>\n<li>On the 20th day of the 9th moon, <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> becomes 16, ending her mother's Regency.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=50_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Marq_Farman\" title=\"Marq Farman\">Marq Farman</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Stark_(Lord)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Walton Stark (Lord)\">Walton Stark</a>, killed while putting down an uprising at the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Olyver_Bracken\" title=\"Olyver Bracken\">Olyver Bracken</a> executed by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Stark_(Lord)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Walton Stark (Lord)\">Walton Stark</a> for mutiny against the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raymund_Mallery\" title=\"Raymund Mallery\">Raymund Mallery</a>, killed by wildlings, north of <a href=\"/index.php/The_Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Wall\">The Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Titles_and_Positions\">Titles and Positions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=50_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Titles and Positions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lucinda_Tully\" title=\"Lucinda Tully\">Lucinda Tully</a> takes charge of <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a>'s household at Dragonstone.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Septa_Ysabel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Septa Ysabel\">Septa Ysabel</a>, aided by novices <a href=\"/index.php/Lyra\" title=\"Lyra\">Lyra</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Edyth\" title=\"Edyth\">Edyth</a>, are entrusted with <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a>'s religious education.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ella_Broome\" title=\"Ella Broome\">Ella Broome</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jennis_Templeton\" title=\"Jennis Templeton\">Jennis Templeton</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Coryanne_Wylde\" title=\"Coryanne Wylde\">Coryanne Wylde</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Rosamund_Ball\" title=\"Rosamund Ball\">Rosamund Ball</a>, and lord Celtigar's two daughters join the queen's household.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a> is dismissed as Hand of the King by his wife, regent <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a>'s tenure as regent ends with the coming of age of king Jaehaerys.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Prentys_Tully\" title=\"Prentys Tully\">Prentys Tully</a> is replaced by <a href=\"/index.php/Albin_Massey\" title=\"Albin Massey\">Albin Massey</a> as Master of Laws.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Edwell_Celtigar\" title=\"Edwell Celtigar\">Edwell Celtigar</a> is replaced by <a href=\"/index.php/Rego_Draz\" title=\"Rego Draz\">Rego Draz</a> as Master of Coin.</li>\n<li>Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Mattheus\" title=\"Mattheus\">Mattheus</a> is dismissed from court by King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I</a>, he was replaced by Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Barth\" title=\"Barth\">Barth</a> who came from <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>. According to the legend, Mattheus passed Barth coming in the other direction whilst crossing the <a href=\"/index.php/Mander\" title=\"Mander\">Mander</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=50_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></